data.description: Rare opportunity to own a home in PRIVATE OWLS ROOST ADDITION nestled amongst the trees.  LONE OAK ISD!! NO CITY TAXES!! This home has been beautifully renovated and sits on 2 acres in the country. An easy escape from the noise and congestion of the city. Enjoy the sounds of nature along with the hummingbirds that are regularly seen on the property. Upgrades include: NEW ROOF (NOV 2023), designer lighting, granite counters, Samsung appliances, Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring, new hardware, upgraded fans, canned lighting and so much more!! Rear garage has an unfinished  bedroom with bath and kitchen. Perfect for visiting family or can be used as a rental for added income. Minutes to the highway, Lake Tawakoni & Lake Fork.
